	<p>Rembolt Ludtke&rsquo;s government law practice area includes in-house and case-specific representation of governmental entities, including cities, counties, natural resources districts, public power and irrigation districts, and the State of Nebraska.  The firm&rsquo;s attorneys practicing in this area understand the unique challenges, constraints, and operations of governmental entities to effectively represent their interests and the interests of their&nbsp;constituents.</p>
<p>This practice area also includes the firm&rsquo;s representation of clients in lobbying governmental bodies and in hearings before governmental agencies.</p>
